The paper deals with feature selection, a common problem in machine learning, which is closely related to the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of deep convolutional featurizers (cs.CV) and proposes a new algorithm (cs.DS) for online streaming feature selection. Finally, the paper introduces a new measure for evaluating feature importance (cs.IT).
